Text.string: Weather report. Cold as hell. What'd you expect? It's space outside, bitches.
Shiiiiiiiiiiit.||—That's all. Keep crewin', crew.
Come on by the bridge and say what's up, crew. This bear needs a squeeze.
S'up, crew? Your main navigator BALEX here, checkin' in. We all cool? Cool.
Listen up. Keep this place clean. No one wants your dirt. Damn. Get serious. This is space, people.
A quick shout out to Claptrap. Nah-nah, I'm just kiddin'. No, nah, I'm not. You're all right, Claptrap. Just watch them stairs though, homie.
Yo, if I catch anyone using the air filtration units as a bottle opener, I'ma throw you out the airlock. Seriously.
Hey, Vault Hunter. Let's go somewhere chill as hell.
I don't know about a falcon, but BALEX got specs for mad parsecs.
Remember. This is space, people. So don't do nothin' stupid.
Emergency! Don't do nothin' stupid.
Shit's goin' down, but BALEX is on it!
Emergency! Be chill, I got this.
Let's navigate, bitches!
BALEX got ya!
Here we go, people.
Damn!
You feel that?
That's some ludicrous speed.
Aight, bitches. Where to next?
Damn, Tannis can phaseshift me any day. You know what I'm talkin' 'bout. I'm talkin' 'bout that crazy, freaky computer stuff.
You killed that little bitch Troy! I knew you would.
The Calypsos are that Typhon dude's kids! I'ma say it—now that's just bad parenting.
It's gettin' real, Vault Hunter. But you got this.
The hero of the galaxy! I knew you were special back when I found you in that swamp.
What's good, Vault Hunter?
You kill some bandits on the ground, I'll keep it safe up here.
Being a teddy bear was cool, but... it's good to be up in Sanctuary. Feels like home.
I was stuck inside a saurian for five days, but I ain't never smelled anything as bad as Earl. Damn.
Back in space! The way it's meant to be! After all that GenIVIV stuff, I ain't plannin' on crashin' again anytime soon.
Hey! Come hang out. I can't bite.
I see you! Come over.
Hey-hey!
Hey, come chill with me.
Vault Hunter. What's up?
You hangin' in there, VH?
The Vault Hunter's rollin' up! What's good?
There you are! What's up?
Yo, Vault Hunter. Give me a squeeze—for old time's sake.
Vault Hunter!
Later.
Aight—back to keepin' your ass alive.
I'll catch you later.
Don't get yourself killed, Vault Hunter.
Stay chill, VH. I got ya.
Peace, Vault Hunter!
Do what you do!
They gonna run when they see you, Vault Hunter!
Don't worry. I got this shit on lock.
Hey, pick me up a new chain while you're out there.
All right, it's the Bloody Harvest. I wanna see costumes, people! Slutty robot, slutty Vault monster, I don't care—just make it slutty!
Bloody Harvest, baby! Spooky time!
Attention, everyone—if I see anyone handing out candy corn, I'mma smack the dumb out of ya.
During Bloody Harvest, all drinking water will now be pumpkin spice flavored. You're welcome.
You can just bring all that candy up to the bridge, y'all.
Mercenary Day! Y'all can leave all my presents on the bridge in a big pile. And if you didn't get me anything, I just wanna remind everyone that I control all the airlocks around here.
Who else is feeling festive as fuck up in here?
If anyone's up for a snowball fight, I'll be venting the reactor coolant into the cargo bay in a little. Just try not to breathe too much.
Who the fuck put this hat on me? I love it.
Aw, damn, I left all my holiday albums in the old ship! Okay, y'all responsible for your own carols.
I don't remember what that shit does, but it's important, so be cool.
That little bitch keeps us breathin'!
What are you doing? You'll KILL US ALL!||—Hahaha, nah, that's some bullshit, don't worry about it.
That engine is the real deal, baby. Hyper-quantum-bullshit. That's what it is, so enjoy the ride.
Hear that engine purring? All me.
You serious? Don't touch that! It's an incredibly expensive dangerous engine!
That's the trash compactor. You better treat it with respect.
One person's trash is another person's trash. Think about that.
